body_html:
Yes, print should have the same behavior as identity (and it does). I'll happily accept a PR to fix the docstring.

I can see how the docstring is confusing if you think a variable is a tensor (it's not). A variable is a thing which can be converted to a tensor containing its current value. It also can be assigned to, partitioned, etc, which tensors can't.
